snippet.title: Super Smash Bros. Ultimate | Playable Bosses Trailer
snippet.description:
The Playable Bosses mod, which is centered around the competitive scene, is finally available for its full release!

We are not legally responsible for what you do with this mod. We do not condone cheating with this mod in a multiplayer environment.

We hope you enjoy this mod!

This mod falls under educational purposes as we have published the source code of the mod for all to study and analyze for their own educational purposes. This in turn follows the fair use law within the United States of America.

Playable Bosses Mod:
GamaBanana: https://gamebanana.com/mods/457095
Source Code: https://github.com/NemesisSSBU/Playable_Bosses
